      "startTime": 281.2506742603743
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あ、はい……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? O-Oh‚ yes… Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.2506742603743,
      "endTime": 285.6082480556929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-asakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-kyi008.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、目を丸くして\n何もおかしなことは言っていないだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with that‚ widening your eyes.\nI didn't say anything strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.8082480556929,
      "endTime": 291.50824815106034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 291.7082480556927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、そうですね\n改めて……ありがとうございます、社長",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ you're right.\nOnce again… thank you‚ President.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.7082480556927,
      "endTime": 298.45824786495785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 298.6582478649576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-krk001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こちらにいらしたんですね、社長\n来月放送予定の歌番組にトリエルをねじ込みました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you're here‚ President.\nI've squeezed TRINITYAiLE into a music program scheduled to air next month.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.6582478649576,
      "endTime": 306.9582478649576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-asakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-kyi009.m4a",
      "text": "姫野……勝手に動くなと言っただろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Himeno… I told you not to act on your own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.15824786495756,
      "endTime": 310.5582477695902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 310.7582477695902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "またいつの間にか仕事増えてるやんか\n休む暇なしやな、ほんまに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our workload has increased again without us knowing.\nWe have no time to rest‚ seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.7582477695902,
      "endTime": 316.77806636166173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-krk002.m4a",
      "text": "当然でしょう\nあなた達は、今が頑張り時で稼ぎ時なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nThis is the time for you to work hard and earn money.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.99085385062114,
      "endTime": 322.95049082495586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 323.15752051728776
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……こういうの、身も蓋もないって言うんだよね\nでも、ありがとうございます姫野さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… This is what they call a harsh truth‚ right?\nBut‚ thank you‚ Himeno-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 323.15752051728776,
      "endTime": 331.97851851838647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 332.1655002388638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "仕事はあるに越したことはありません\nそのたびに私達は、もっともっと近づけると思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more work‚ the better.\nI believe that with each opportunity‚ we can get closer and closer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 332.1655002388638,
      "endTime": 339.1729377541226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-krk003.m4a",
      "text": "近づける？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Closer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.3655002388636,
      "endTime": 340.62688346239725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 341.0321669055303
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui030.m4a",
      "text": "私達が目指す、トップアイドルに……です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To the top idol… that we aim to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.0321669055303,
      "endTime": 345.43216681016287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 345.63216681016286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kiriko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-krk004.m4a",
      "text": "……ええ、そうね。そうでなくちゃ困るわ\n頑張ってね、私も可能な範囲でサポートするから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ that's right. You better be.\nWork hard‚ I'll support you as much as I can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 345.63216681016286,
      "endTime": 354.7452962352117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 355.2321668101628
    },
    {
